title: Disney Princess Stories Vol 2 Enchanted Tea Party (bouncinbunny)
description: In a beautiful palace garden, under a shining sapphire sky, the most delightful celebration in all the land is about to begin. It&#039;s an enchanted royal tea party, and your little princess is the guest of honor! On the wings of music and magic, your child will discover a lovely kingdom of happiness, harmony, and dreams come true. There, she can sing along with all her favorite Disney Princesses as they perform their best-loved songs from Disney&#039;s award-winning classics. Plus, she&#039;ll be the belle of the ball as she learns wonderful dance moves and sings karaoke-style too! So give your little girl the crown jewels of Disney&#039;s musical library, and let the enchantment reign forever and a day.
